JAVAFX NOTES:


FXML CODE:

FOR PICTURES TO WORK IMG URL Should have forward slashes not back slashes
example: "file:/C:/Users/rellik/SyntacticalDA/picture.jpeg"



Also Make sure the Controller is connected via scene builder for methods to be utilized and 
the controller classes are in the same packages as the views FXML files


TextAREAS:
make sure your .txt files are not open while running application. will cause interrupting
and might not load correctly

Static methods to retain SQL row values


WORKING ON ONE CONTROLLER FOR ALL DISPLAYS 